				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 16 Apr 2018 19:46:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>AgentWilson</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>802114</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm not a fan of the first item in the list - the part about it turning into a whole pineapple that causes internal hemorrhaging, which is expected for having a whole pineapple suddenly appearing inside your body but not in line with the rest of the items. And the interview showing either blatant ignorance or willful maliciousness - either she's actively ignoring that people are dying from having a large, spiny fruit make them bleed to death, or she's trying to cause that to happen. She says it's so the &quot;regulars&quot; won't complain, but I don't see how you can have anybody order the item regularly if they all die.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
